File: The suspects face a combined 188 counts of theft, corruption, money laundering and racketeering.(AFP) JOHANNESBURG - The Hawks have arrested five people allegedly linked to the VBS looting scandal. Those arrested include senior personnel at VBS as well as an ANC Limpopo official. READ: VBS case postponed, more charges and arrests anticipated The suspects face a combined 188 counts of theft, corruption, money laundering and racketeering. 